</span></p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-fulBNO eRdNQN pf-123_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-kMriOJ bmOeBq pf-124_"><strong>The Good Grief Trust </strong>- Provides an extensive directory of support services across the UK for bereavement.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-kMriOJ bmOeBq pf-126_"><strong>Cruse Bereavement Support</strong> - Offers tailored counselling and advice to individuals coping with loss.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-kMriOJ bmOeBq pf-128_"><strong>Mind UK</strong> - Addresses the mental health impacts of grief and provides resources for emotional well-being.
</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jXbVAB kNtuek pf-130_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dExXmK fNpoDq pf-131_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cmaqZA fXrIOS pf-132_">Conclusion
